    SELECT TOP(1) [i].[Id], [i].[CategoryId], [i].[Description], [i].[ItemName], [i].[Price], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CategoryName]
    FROM [Items] AS [i]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [i].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [i].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i0] ON [t].[Id] = [i0].[ItemId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]

2024-04-16 15:04:17.554 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[@__id_0='1'], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CustomerId], [t].[OrderDate], [t].[Status], [t].[Id0], [t].[AddressId], [t].[Email], [t].[FirstName], [t].[LastName], [t].[Phone], [t].[UserId], [t].[Id1], [t].[Email0], [t].[Password], [t].[Roleid], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ItemId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Status], [t0].[WarehouseId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[Description], [t0].[ItemName], [t0].[Price]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CustomerId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[AddressId], [c].[Email], [c].[FirstName], [c].[LastName], [c].[Phone], [c].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id1], [u].[Email] AS [Email0], [u].[Password], [u].[Roleid]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c] ON [o].[CustomerId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [c].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
    WHERE [o].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[ItemId], [i].[OrderId], [i].[Quantity], [i].[Status], [i].[WarehouseId], [i0].[Id] AS [Id0], [i0].[CategoryId], [i0].[Description], [i0].[ItemName], [i0].[Price]
    FROM [ItemOrders] AS [i]
    INNER JOIN [Items] AS [i0] ON [i].[ItemId] = [i0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [c].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
    WHERE [o].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id]
